{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/fa9w3m94","slide":3,"text":"Limitations of current AI models","textPreview":"Limitations of current AI models","textChars":32,"textLines":1,"bbox":[72,88,880,92]}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/qpg3ex0n","slide":3,"bbox":[90,218,9,9]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/x4nap4r6","slide":3,"text":"Limited continuity: models rarely carry a durable understanding across tools and sessions.","textPreview":"Limited continuity: models rarely carry a durable understanding across tools and sessions.","textChars":90,"textLines":1,"bbox":[114,210,476,70]}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/8jqh0fep","slide":3,"bbox":[90,292,9,9]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/fyxobm58","slide":3,"text":"Context-window dependence: users must paste, summarize, or re-upload history to get useful answers.","textPreview":"Context-window dependence: users must paste, summarize, or re-upload history to get useful answers.","textChars":99,"textLines":1,"bbox":[114,284,476,70]}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/qd4vmtwr","slide":3,"bbox":[90,366,9,9]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/xs72x4na","slide":3,"text":"Weak provenance: outputs often lack source-backed memory, timestamps, and confidence.","textPreview":"Weak provenance: outputs often lack source-backed memory, timestamps, and confidence.","textChars":85,"textLines":1,"bbox":[114,358,476,70]}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/87ed8bat","slide":3,"bbox":[90,440,9,9]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/ed8v6psf","slide":3,"text":"Blunt personalization: assistants infer preferences from recent conversation instead of a governed identity graph.","textPreview":"Blunt personalization: assistants infer preferences from recent conversation instead of a governed identity graph.","textChars":114,"textLines":1,"bbox":[114,432,476,70]}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/7y1kre1w","slide":3,"bbox":[680,218,9,9]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/wjudg7ad","slide":3,"text":"Privacy tradeoff: richer personalization often requires giving one platform more raw data.","textPreview":"Privacy tradeoff: richer personalization often requires giving one platform more raw data.","textChars":90,"textLines":1,"bbox":[704,210,476,70]}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/p4r65wju","slide":3,"bbox":[680,292,9,9]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/i5sneloj","slide":3,"text":"No shared user layer: each AI app builds its own isolated memory and permission model.","textPreview":"No shared user layer: each AI app builds its own isolated memory and permission model.","textChars":86,"textLines":1,"bbox":[704,284,476,70]}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/7qpg3ex0","slide":3,"bbox":[680,366,9,9]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/0bi9s36h","slide":3,"text":"Poor correction loop: users cannot easily inspect, revise, or revoke what the model remembers.","textPreview":"Poor correction loop: users cannot easily inspect, revise, or revoke what the model remembers.","textChars":94,"textLines":1,"bbox":[704,358,476,70]}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/pwb2hwfy","slide":3,"bbox":[680,440,9,9]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/itgfmlkj","slide":3,"text":"No least-privilege routing: different agents cannot receive exactly the context they need and nothing more.","textPreview":"No least-privilege routing: different agents cannot receive exactly the context they need and nothing more.","textChars":107,"textLines":1,"bbox":[704,432,476,70]}
